### Improved Visual Studio .gitignore ###
# Based on https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore
# Last updated: 2023-10-15

# =========================================
# Important: If you have already committed files that are now ignored,
# run these commands to clean your repository:
#   git rm -r --cached .
#   git add .
#   git commit -m "Clean up ignored files"
# =========================================

